
### new accounts
POST http://localhost:9899/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "wuyue",
  "currency": "USD"
}

### get account
GET http://localhost:9899/accounts/2


### get account list
GET http://localhost:9899/accounts?page_id=1&page_size=5



### create transfer
POST http://localhost:9899/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_account_id": 1,
  "to_account_id": 2,
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD"
}
